text: Limpedea may refer to the following rivers in Romania: * Limpedea, a tributary of the Trebeș in Bacău County * Limpedea, a tributary of the Băița in Maramureș County * Limpedea, a tributary of the Berindești in Argeș County * Limpedea, a tributary of the Izvorul Alb in Suceava County
title: Limpedea (disambiguation)
